rows.label: qst701709_msg0002
rows.name:
Well, yes... But I think there's been
some kind of mistake.

rows.label: qst701709_msg0003
rows.name:
A mistake? Wait. Don't tell me the
culprit's someone you know!

rows.label: qst701709_msg0004
rows.name:
Out with it! I wanna know who did it!
Tell me right now, or so help me-

rows.label: qst701709_msg0005
rows.name:
Look, just chill out.
The name we got was Dio, the
handyman. You must know him too?

rows.label: qst701709_msg0007
rows.name:
Oh, but he didn't kill your sister!
Actually, it was the oppo-

rows.label: qst701709_msg0010
rows.name:
I'm sorry it fell to you to break
the news...

rows.label: qst701709_msg0011
rows.name:
I don't care and you shouldn't either.
If I hadn't stepped up, I'm pretty sure
Shin would've cut the guy's head off..

rows.label: qst701709_msg0012
rows.name: What idiotic flight of fancy is that?

rows.label: qst701709_msg0013
rows.name:
Come now, that kind of attitude
won't do, Shin

rows.label: qst701709_msg0015
rows.name:
Let's stop squabbling and get to
Dio's place - quick!
